data.description: Come tour this beautifully updated 3 bedroom/2.5 bath home nestled on a large 1 acre lot just steps from Glendale! This stylish property features a beautiful kitchen with new appliances and a spacious living area with gorgeous laminate wood flooring that extends up the stairs. Upgrades include replacement windows throughout the home (transferable warranty); added a back patio that is maintenance free; leaf filter guards along the top gutters that makes cleaning a breeze; smart garage opener w/camera and Amazon key in garage delivery; and fiber optic internet. The second-floor houses all the bedrooms and the two full baths (toilets have been replaced throughout the home and a new vanity has been installed in the spare bathroom. Travel to the basement to discover a second living area and large storage area.
